00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:42,920
that if one big drug company goes out of business in Denmark, for example,

35
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:47,970
there are going to be other enterprises that are there to provide

36
00:02:47,970 --> 00:02:52,410
