00:04:07,810 --> 00:04:09,250
other way around.

52
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:14,770
So the theory is that some small societies are going to develop a kind

53
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:22,630
of a sensing system that is going to alert decision makers to changes in

54
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:28,160
conditions in the outside world to a greater degree than would be the case

55
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:31,660
in most larger countries, which feel less vulnerable.

56
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:38,330
And the result of that very careful attention that is being paid to

57
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:44,980
conditions outside the small country can pay off in terms of decision

58
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:49,620
making benefits about, well, we'd better get out of that market, it

